atforms for marketing and demos</li>\n                <li>Direct sales teams for enterprise engagements</li>\n                <li>Partnerships and integrations with tech providers</li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"section cost-structure\">\n            <h2 data-emoji=\"💰\">Cost Structure</h2>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Software development and maintenance expenses</li>\n                <li>Team salaries for technical and sales roles</li>\n                <li>Marketing and customer acquisition costs</li>\n                <li>Operational costs for tools and infrastructure</li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"section revenue-streams\">\n            <h2 data-emoji=\"📈\">Revenue Streams</h2>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Subscription fees for energy management software</li>\n                <li>Licensing agreements for enterprise use</li>\n                <li>Service-based revenue from custom integrations</li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <footer>Generated by AI Business Coach - October 5, 2023</footer>\n</body>\n</html>",
