r demos and customer engagement.</li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"bottom-row\">\n            <div class=\"section cost-structure\">\n                <h2>💰 Cost Structure</h2>\n                <ul>\n                    <li>Employee salaries for technical and sales teams.</li>\n                    <li>Development and maintenance of software tools.</li>\n                    <li>Marketing and operational expenses for B2B outreach.</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"section revenue-streams\">\n                <h2>💵 Revenue Streams</h2>\n                <ul>\n                    <li>Subscription fees for energy management services.</li>\n                    <li>Enterprise contracts and premium feature add-ons.</li>\n                    <li>Partnership commissions and consulting services.</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n        Generated by AI Business Coach - October 5, 2023\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>",
